description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10 minute FEISTY & FUN Full Body Workout with Dumbbells' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Strength.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: FUN, FEISTY, and ONLY 10 MINUTES!? YES PLEASE! This is a short, intense, and effective full body workout when you want to work it all!

I know with school starting back up, exercise time in the morning might be cut short. This workout is perfect when you are short on time, but don't want to miss out on an awesome workout! Things do move quickly during this workout, so before we end each exercise I will let you know what we have coming next, you can also see the full work structure below!

FEISTY AND FUN FULL BODY WORKOUT EQUIPMENT, STRUCTURE, AND EXERCISES

EQUIPMENT: DUMBBELLS AND A MAT
I'm using 5kg, 7.5kg, 10kg, & 17.5kg.

WORKOUT STRUCTURE
9 EXERCISES
1 TIME THROUGH EACH EXERCISE
WORK: 60 REST: 10
 
EXERCISE  LIST (MODIFICATIONS WILL BE INCLUDED FOR SOME OF THE EXERCISES)

EXERCISE LIST
- TRICEP OVERHEAD EXTENSION
- CURL AND PRESS
- SUMO SQUAT
- PUSH UPS
- DEAD BUG
- SUMO GLUTE BRIDGE
- GOBLET SQUAT
- RENEGADE ROWS
- BICYCLE CRUNCH
 
Don't forget to complete a proper warm-up before...
